quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  18,84,Ndithudi Ife tidamukhazika iye padziko ndipo tidamupatsa njira yopezera chilichonse
  18,85,Ndipo iye adatsatira njira
  18,86,"Mpaka pamene adafika polowera dzuwa ndipo adalipeza dzuwalo lili kulowa m’dziwe la matope akuda. Pafupi pomwepo iye adapeza anthu ena. Ife tidati, “Iwe Dhul-Qarnain! Iwe uli ndi ufulu wowalanga kapena wowachitira chisoni.”"
  18,87,"Iye adati, “Akakhala iye amene achita zoipa, tidzamulanga ndipo iye adzabwezedwa kwa Ambuye wake yemwe adzamulanga ndi chilango choipa kwambiri.”"
  18,88,"Koma iye amene wakhulupirira ndikumachita ntchito zabwino, adzakhala ndi mphotho yabwino ndipo tidzamuyankhula mawu abwino"
  18,89,Ndipo iye adatsatira njira ina
  18,90,Mpaka pamene adafika kotulukira dzuwa kumene adalipeza dzuwa lili kutuluka pa anthu amene Ife sitidawaikire chotchinga ku dzuwa
  18,91,Kotero Ife tidadziwa zonse zokhudza iye
  18,92,Ndipo iye adatsatiranso njira ina
  18,93,Mpaka pamene iye adafika pakati pa mapiri awiri adapeza pambali pake anthu amene sanali kuzindikira chilichonse
  18,94,"Iwo adati, “Iwe Dhul-Qarnain! Ndithudi Ya-juj ndi Majuj ali kuchita zoipa m’dziko lino. Kodi tikupatse malipiro kuti utimangire linga lotiteteza nalo pakati pa iwo ndi ife?”"
  18,95,"Iye adati, “Mphamvu zomangira linga zimene Ambuye wanga wandipatsa ndi zabwino. Choncho ndithandizeni ndi anthu amphamvu ogwira ntchito kuti ndimange linga pakati pa inu ndi iwo.”"
  18,96,"Ndipatseni zidutswa zachitsulo; mpaka pamene iye adadzadza gawo limene linali pakati pa mapiriwa. Iye adati, “Uzirani ndi livumbo lanu.” Pamene adazifiwiritsa zidutswazo ngati moto, iye adati, “Ndipatseni mtovu kuti ndiuthire pa zidutswazo.”"
  18,97,Anthu a Ya-juj ndi Majuj sadathe kuchilumpha ndipo sadathe kuchiboola